(4, 3, 'Finay III Sezonu Wargaming.net League Europe w Tychach!', '', 0, '2014-01-14 17:00:00', '2014-01-26 17:00:00', 'Wielkimi krokami, zblia si batalia midzy najlepszymi zespoami World of Tanks w Europie. Sze zespow, ktre uzbieray najwicej punktw w fazie online Wargaming.net League EU, zjawi si w Browarze Obywatelskim w Tychach! Tam powalcz o mistrzowski tytu i zwycistwo w trzecim sezonie rozgrywek WGL. Impreza odbdzie si midzy 24 a 25 stycznia - za organizacje oraz stream z turnieju odpowiada ekipa ESL.TV Polska! \r\n\r\nChcesz zapisa si do turnieju ?! http://forum.worldoftanks.eu/index.php?/topic/341870-zapisy-na-finaly-trzeciego-sezonu-wgl-eu-w-tychach/\r\n\r\nFinay III Sezonu Wargaming.net League Europe: http://www.twitch.tv/esltv_wot\r\n24 - 25 stycznia, na ywo w ESL.TV: http://www.twitch.tv/esltv_wot\r\n\r\nJeli chciaby dowiedzie si wicej o rozgrywkach WGL koniecznie zajrzyj na http://wgleu.com/', 'The European Season 3 Finals are just around the corner and with it comes the final chance for players to qualify for the Global Finals in Poland. The six best teams in Europe will battle it out in Tychy, Poland on the 24th and the 25th of January to decide who will make it to the Global Finals.', 'http://', ''),
(5, 1, 'LCS EU - 2014 Spring Split', '', 0, '2014-01-16 21:00:00', '2014-07-13 00:00:00', 'League of Legends Championship Series Europe', 'League of Legends Championship Series Europe', 'http://eune.lolesports.com/', '52d834527c287.jpg'),
(6, 3, 'WOT PRO LEAGUE: FINALS', '', 0, '2014-01-19 13:37:00', '2015-01-19 13:35:00', 'Pierwszy mecz Finau WOT PRO LEAGUE rozpocznie si 24.01. 12:10h.\r\nO awans powalczy druyna Evil Panda Squad i Lemming Train.\r\n \r\n\r\n \r\nEvil Panda Squad', 'The third season of the Wargaming.net League has shown us some amazing games and it is all culminating for the season finals! On the 24th and 25th of January the six best teams of Europe will battle it out in Tychy, Poland for their slice of the 100,000 prizepool.', 'http://wgleu.com/season3/finals/', ''),
