(1, 'fnatic', 'fnatic', '2013-09-08 17:55:44', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522c9e00d3899.png', 'http://www.fnatic.com/', 'Druyna Fnatic jest wiatowym liderem w wielu grach takich jak League of Legends, Dota 2, Halo i innych. Nasi zawodnicy uczestnicz w ponad 75 wydarzeniach rocznie, odbywajcych si w ponad 25 krajach. \r\nPonad 1,200,000 uytkownikw ledzi nas tylko przez social media, dziesitki tysicy oglda streamy na ywo, bd nasze filmy.\r\n\r\nW Europie, Stanach Zjednoczonych, Indiach i Ameryce Poudniowej, Fnatic jest uwaany za najlepszy e-sportowy zesp, co ma odzwierciedlenie w ilo wygranych turniejw. Zwycistwa w ESPORTS Team of the Year Award w 2006 i 2009 roku tylko to potwierdzaj.\r\n\r\nZespoem zarzdzaj Sam Mathews, Anne Mathews a nasze biuro znajduje si w Londynie. Wizja i cel nie mog zosta osignite przez jedn osob. To dlatego personel dba o jak najszerszy zasig kadej imprezy, zawodnikw, uczestnikw i zawsze stara si informowa naszych fanw o najnowszych wynikach, aktualnociach, wywiadach i spostrzeeniach.\r\n\r\nrdo: http://www.fnatic.com/about', 'The team Fnatic is the world leader in multiple games such as League of Legends, Dota 2, Halo and more. Our players attend more than 75 events per year, representing the ideals of Fnatic in over 25 countries. More than 1,200,000 fans, only on the social media, follow us and get the latest information about the Stars. Hundreds of thousands watch the games on streams and VoDs.\r\n\r\nIn Europe, the US, India and South America, Fnatic stands for the best eSports team, whos players achieved numerous tournament wins. Winning the ESPORTS Team of the Year Award in 2006 and 2009 gives only a small prove to how sophisticated the team is in their cohesion and practise.\r\n\r\nThe management around founders Sam Mathews, Anne Mathews is resident in London, where our main office is located. The vision and goal can not be achieved by a single person. This is why the staff takes care of a flawless coverage of every event the players attend and always tries to bring our fans the latest scores, news, interviews and insights.\r\n\r\nhttp://www.fnatic.com/about'),
(2, 'SK Gaming', 'SK', '2013-09-08 18:10:03', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522ca15b4038f.png', 'http://www.sk-gaming.com/', 'SK Gaming jest midzynarodow organizacj multi-gamingow, ktra zgromadzi nie tylko najlepszych graczy z rznych gier, ale take pozyskuje nadchodzce talenty zapewniajc im odpowiedni trening. SK Gaming zosta zaoony w 1997 roku pod nazw &quot;Schroet Kommando&quot; w Oberhausen w Niemczech.\r\n\r\nDzi, z siedzib w Kolonii, w Niemczech i Sztokholmie, w Szwecji i z profesjonalnymi pracownikami, SK Gaming sta si redni firm.  Obszary dziaania obejmuj zarzdzanie profesjonalnymi graczami, esportow spoeczno, sprzeday towarw i promocja e-sportu na caym wiecie. Ponad 50 najlepszych zawodowych graczy jest zwizanych z SK.\r\n\r\nSK ewoluowao z klanu w profesjonalny biznes. Ludzi stojcych za mark SK Gaming czy jedno: maj one ogromne zamiowanie do sportw elektronicznych, pragnienie, aby by najlepszym w kadym calu, wol i ambicj, aby pracowa nad tym kadego dnia.\r\n\r\nrdo: http://www.sk-gaming.com/', 'SK Gaming is an international multi-gaming organisation, gathering together not only the top players of each gaming discipline but also nurturing upcoming talent and making them the stars of today. SK Gaming was founded in 1997 under the name \\\\\\\\\\\\\\''Schroet Kommando\\\\\\\\\\\\\\'' in Oberhausen, Germany.\r\n\r\nToday, with offices in Cologne, Germany and Stockholm, Sweden and a professional and innovative employee structure, SK Gaming has become a medium-sized business. Business areas include the management of professional esports players, online community, sales of fan merchandise, and promotional events all over the world. More than 50 of today\\\\\\\\\\\\\\''s top professional eSports gamers are with SK Gaming and the basis of the clan\\\\\\\\\\\\\\''s success.\r\n\r\nSK has grown from esport clan into a professional business. The people behind the SK Gaming brand have all one thing in common: they share a huge passion for esports, the desire to be the best at all times and the will and ambition to work at it every day.\r\n\r\nrdo: http://www.sk-gaming.com/'),
(5, 'Gambit Gaming BenQ', 'Gambit', '2013-09-08 18:32:14', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522ca68e11a0d.png', 'http://gambit-gaming.com/', 'Gambit Gaming jest europejsk druyn e-sportow utworzon w styczniu 2013 roku w miejsce Moscow Five.\r\n\r\nObecnie zawodnicy wystpuj pod nazw Gaming BenQ reprezentujc swojego sponsora.\r\n\r\nrdo: http://lol.gamepedia.com/Gambit_Gaming', 'Gambit Gaming is a European Esports organization formed in January 2013 after the acquisition of the previous roster of Moscow Five.\r\n\r\nThe team currently competes under the name Gambit Gaming BenQ in representation of their sponsor.\r\n\r\nvia:  http://lol.gamepedia.com/Gambit_Gaming'),
(6, 'Ninja in Pyjamas', 'NiP', '2013-09-08 18:40:51', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522ca893c4fc1.png', 'http://www.nip-gaming.se', 'Ninjas in Pyjamas zosta zaoony w czerwcu 2000 roku, ale ostatecznie jako zesp dziaa od 2001 roku, po kilku zmianach nazw.\r\n\r\nIch najwikszym sukcesem byo zdobycie w 2001 Cyberathlete Professional League World Championships. Wkrtce po tym NiP mia problemy ze znalezieniem sponsora. Rozwizanie nadeszo od strony SK Gaming, do ktrej doczyli i przez pewien czas wystpowali jako SK Scandinavia i SK Sveden w tym samym czasie. W SK kontynuowali swj sukces i stali si dominujc si w Counter-Strike.Nagrody z ich zwycistw turniejowych w 2003 r. wynosiy okoo 170.000 dolarw.\r\n\r\nW 2013 roku podczas rozgrywek playoff na Gamescom dostali si do wiatowego finau [b]League of Legends Championship Series[/b].\r\n\r\nrdo: http://www.nip-gaming.se/about/', 'Ninjas in Pyjamas was originally formed in June 2000, but was solidified as a team in 2001 after several lineup changes and namechanges.\r\n\r\nTheir biggest success was winning the 2001 Cyberathlete Professional League World Championships after a very close final with X3 (a forerunner to Team 3D). Soon after this they had trouble finding sponsors but the solution came when they joined the prominent e-sports organization SK Gaming and were known by the names SK Scandinavia and SK Sweden during their time there. At SK they continued their success and became a dominant force in Counter-Strike. The prize money from their tournament victories in 2003 totalled approximately 170,000 U.S. dollars.\r\n\r\nEmil Christensen, together with co-player and friend Tommy Potti Ingemarssen, managing directors Peter Hedlund and Victor Lindqvist reformed NiP as a Swedish stockcompany in 2005. The reformed NiP continued their participation in international tournaments, placing high in many of the events they attended. Emil Christensen, Peter Hedlund and Victor Lindqvist managed to take the company to the next level by closing some of the biggest sponsorship deals in the scene so far. They got about 100 000 members on their international e-sport community website in Europe during their first two years and was also the first Counter-Strike team, not from Asia, to enter the Asian market. Within six months they had about 90 000 members on their Asian website.\r\n\r\nOn the 10th of August 2012 Ninjas in Pyjamas announced their comeback by switching from CS 1.6 to CS: Global Offensive. Going into the new chapter of professional Counter-Strike couldnt have gone better for NiP. In the first 6 months of CS:GO the team consisting of Christopher GeT_RiGhT Alesund , Patrik f0rest Lindberg, Richard Xizt Landstrm, Adam Friberg Friberg and Robin Fifflaren Johansson hasnt lost a single map on Lan. They won all the events they attended including DreamHack Winter and ESWC 2012! Therefore Ninjas in Pyjamas is the first ever World Champion in Counter-Strike: Global Offensive.  On the 4th of April the first map loss on Lan occurred and it was also the first time NiP didnt win the tournament they attended. Since then this happened just once at the EMS One Summer Finals in Cologne and NiP won tournaments such as the SLTV StarSeries VI Finals or DreamHack Summer!\r\n\r\nWith the arrival of a League of Legends team on the 22nd of May 2013 Ninjas in Pyjamas opened a new chapter in their history books. During that time this Lineup was a very promising one, consisting of Sren Bjergsen Bjerg, Martin Deficio Lynge, Kasper Thetess Poulsen, Dennis Svenskeren Johnsen and Dan Neegodbro Vo. After disappointing results in the LCS Summer Split, 3 members of the team stepped down and 3 new players were acquired. With Vytautas extinkt Melinauskas, Ale Freeze Knnek and Tobias Malunoo Magnusson coming into the team the results started to get better and better. Just when the things were looking good the recently added Vytautas extinkt Melinauskas decided to focus on studying and therefore another new player had to be found. This player was found in the form of Mimer Mimer Ahlstrm. Ninjas in Pyjamas finished the LCS Summer Split on the 5th rank and will therefore fight for a spot in the world finals of LCS Summer during Gamescom 2013!\r\n\r\nvia http://www.nip-gaming.se/about/'),
(7, 'mousesports', 'mouz', '2013-09-08 19:07:12', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522caec03c6c2.png', 'http://www.mousesports.com/', 'mousesports, znane jako mouz jest niemieckim multi-gamingiem ktry powsta w 2002 roku jako zesp Counter Strike. Osignli liczne sukcesy w CS, Quake 4, Warcraft 3.\r\n\r\nObecnie wystpuj w rozgrywkach Starcraft 2, League of Legends, World of Tanks, Pro Evolution Soccer,  Trackmania, Dota 2.', 'mousesports, often abbreviated mouz, is a German multigaming organisation which was founded in 2002 as a Counter-Strike team.'),
(8, 'Team ALTERNATE', 'ALTERNATE', '2013-09-08 19:14:32', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522cb077f0310.png', 'http://www.team-alternate.de/', 'Team ALTERNATE jest niemieck organizacj gamingow uczestniczc w rozgrywach League of Legends, Counter Strike: Source, Starcraft II i Fifa.', 'Team ALTERNATE is a German based gaming organization that sponsors teams in League of Legends, Counter Strike: Source, Starcraft II, and racing games.'),
(9, 'Evil Geniuses', 'EG', '2013-09-08 23:08:51', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522ce76337440.png', 'http://evilgeniuses.gg/', 'Zaoona w 1999 roku, Evil Geniuses stworzone z myl o profesjonalnych graczach. Prowadzi transmisje online i offline, rozwija unikalne inicjatywy marketingowych majcych na celu przycignicie i zaciekawienie graczy. \r\nZe wsparciem popularnych marek takich jak Intel, Monster Energy, Kingston HyperX i inni, EG wyrs na profesjonalny zesp w Ameryce Pnocnej i sta si wiatowym liderem w dziedzinie e-sportu.\r\n\r\nZawodnicy i druyny w EG takich jak Justin &quot;JWong&quot; Wong i Izaaka &quot;Azael&quot; Cummings-Bentley, zdobyli trofea mistrzowskie we wszystkich waniejszych turniejach gier na wiecie i nadal kontynuuj swoj dominacj w wiecie esportu.', 'Founded in 1999, Evil Geniuses (Team EG) have grown to become a leading new media agency which specializes in contracting pro gamers, executing online and offline broadcasts, and developing unique marketing initiatives aimed at attracting and influencing gamers worldwide.With support from popular brands such as Intel, Monster Energy, Kingston HyperX, and others, EG are North Americas premier professional gaming team and a world leader in e-sports. Players and teams within EG, such as Justin JWong Wong and Isaac Azael Cummings-Bentley, have brought home championship trophies from every major gaming tournament circuit in the world and continue to be influential leaders of gamers everywhere.'),
(10, 'Supa Hot Crew', 'SHC', '2013-09-08 23:24:14', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522ceafebb1e2.png', '', '', ''),
(11, 'MeetYourMakers', 'MYM', '2013-09-08 23:32:13', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522cecdd88d2e.png', '', 'MeetYourMakers GmbH jest redniej wielkoci multi-gamingow midzynarodow organizacj z siedzib w Bensheim, Niemcy. MeetYourMakers jest znany z utalentowanych graczy, ktrzy bior udzia w ponad 20 imprezach w roku na caym wiecie.\r\n\r\nPodczas gdy MYM stanow zawodnicy i uczestnicz w rozgrywkach na wiatowym poziomie, myMYM.com skupia si na promocji eSportu, turniejach, nowociach i spoecznoci takich gier jak Counter-Strike, StarCraft, FIFA, DOTA i League of Legends.\r\n\r\n Redaktorzy zostaj wysyani po caym wiecie, s na wydarzeniach goszczcych od USA do Chin. myMYM zosta nominowany dwa razy z rzdu do nagrody eSports Award w latach 2007 i 2008, ktre byy rozdawane przez Electronic Sports League.', 'The MeetYourMakers GmbH is an medium-sized international multi-gaming organisation based in Bensheim, Germany. MeetYourMakers is known for having talented players around the globe, who take part on more than 20 events in a year. While MYM describes the players and teams, myMYM.com describes the website which focuses on eSports coverage, tournaments, content and community for certain games such as Counter-Strike, Starcraft, FIFA, DotA and League of Legends. Editors and staff have been sent around the globe to cover events ranging from USA to China. During its peak myMYM was known as one of the most important content pages for Warcraft 3, Starcraft, and DotA related news, articles and special video productions. Later on myMYM got nominated two times in a row for the eSports Award in 2007 and 2008 which was given away by the Electronic Sports League.'),
