(22, '1SBP Ulanska Fantazja', 'Ulani', '2013-09-09 15:00:20', '0000-00-00', 'true', 'files/images/logos/522dc6644a9b6.jpg', '', 'Zesp powsta prawie dwa lata temu. Przez ponad dwa miesice od lutego do maja 2012 druyna przesza wiele zmian by wrci do gry podczas ESL Go4WoT Cup#47. \r\n\r\nOd tego czasu zawodnicy pracowali aby dosta si na szczyt. W padzierniku 2012 zmienili nazw na 1SBP Ulanska Fantazja. Moglimy oglda ich zmagania podczas IEM w Spodku w Katowicach.\r\n\r\nObecnie walcz w WoT Pro League.', 'The team was formed almost two years ago and the most significant change we have gone through since then was between February and May of 2012. There had been shifts in command and team members that after 2 month break brought us back onto the ESL stage during Go4WoT Cup #47. Since then we gradually worked our way up to the ladder. Another big change was in October 2012 when we decided to change our team name to \\''1SBP Ulanska Fantazja\\'' which you could see during IEM tournament in Katowice and today.'),
